Gnome2::Panel
=============

This module allows you to create applets for the GNOME 2.0 Panel using Perl.

INSTALLATION
------------

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES
------------

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  perl                >= 5.8.0
  ExtUtils::Depends   >= 0.20  (Perl module)
  ExtUtils::PkgConfig >= 1.03  (Perl module)
  Glib                >= 1.160 (Perl module and requisite C libraries)
  Gtk2                >= 1.040 (Perl module and requisite C libraries)
  Gnome2              >= 1.042 (Perl module and requisite C libraries)
  Gnome2::GConf       >= 1.044 (Perl module and requisite C libraries)
  libpanelapplet-2.0  >= 2.0   (C library)


